    <a href="/2020/04/florida-surgeon-general-suspiciously" title="Florida Surgeon General Suspiciously Silenced After Contradicting DeSantis On Coronavirus">
      <img src="https://videocafe.crooksandliars.com/files/imagecache/node_teaser/mediaposters/2020/04/44835.jpg" alt="Florida Surgeon General Suspiciously Silenced After Contradicting DeSantis On Coronavirus" class="card-img-top" />
